name: Probing Vision Transformers
shortDescription: In this repository, we provide tools to probe into the representations learned by different families of Vision Transformers (supervised pre-training with ImageNet-21k, ImageNet-1k, distillation, etc.)
longDescription: In this repository, we provide tools to probe into the representations learned by different families of Vision Transformers (supervised pre-training with ImageNet-21k, ImageNet-1k, distillation, etc.)
